<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login WarungPOS</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbff 0%, #eef4ff 100%);
      color: #0f172a;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1080px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(360px, 460px);
      border-radius: 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.14);
    }
    .brand {
      padding: 56px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 50%, #0f172a 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      position: relative;
    }
    .brand::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -80px -120px auto;
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      filter: blur(6px);
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .brand h1 {
      margin: 20px 0 14px;
      font-size: 44px;
      line-height: 1.08;
    }
    .brand p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 460px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .brand-list {
      margin: 36px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .brand-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .brand-dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #bfdbfe;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.12);
    }
    .panel {
      padding: 48px 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .back-link {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .panel h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }
    .panel-copy {
      margin: 10px 0 28px;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .message {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .message-error {
      background: #fef2f2;
      color: #b91c1c;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
    }
    .message-success {
      background: #ecfdf5;
      color: #047857;
      border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #334155;
    }
    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border: 1px solid #dbe4f0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font: inherit;
      color: #0f172a;
      background: #f8fbff;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #60a5fa;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.18);
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    button {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      font: inherit;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
    }
    .auth-link {
      margin-top: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .auth-link a {
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .brand { display: none; }
      .panel { padding: 36px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shell">
    <section class="brand">
      <span class="badge">WarungPOS Access</span>
      <h1>Masuk ke dashboard operasional WarungPOS.</h1>
      <p>Gunakan akun yang sudah terdaftar untuk mengakses panel sesuai role Anda, mulai dari manager, operator, kasir, sampai konsumen.</p>
      <ul class="brand-list">
        <li><span class="brand-dot"></span> Warna dan visual selaras dengan landing page</li>
        <li><span class="brand-dot"></span> Satu akun langsung diarahkan ke dashboard role yang sesuai</li>
        <li><span class="brand-dot"></span> Landing page publik ada di halaman utama `/`</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">Kembali ke Landing Page</a>
      <h2>Login</h2>
      <p class="panel-copy">Masukkan email dan password akun Anda untuk masuk ke sistem.</p>

      <% if (typeof flash !== "undefined" && flash && flash.type === "success") { %>
        <div class="message message-success"><%= flash.message %></div>
      <% } %>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="message message-error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/login" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            value="<%= oldInput.email %>"
            placeholder="nama@email.com"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="password">Password</label>
          <input
            type="password"
            id="password"
            name="password"
            placeholder="Masukkan password"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Masuk Sekarang</button>
      </form>

      <p class="auth-link">
        Belum punya akun konsumen? <a href="/register">Daftar di sini</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
